title: Ranking the 2004 QB Class & Early MVP predictions
itunes:title: Ranking the 2004 QB Class & Early MVP predictions
description:
Dave Dameshek is alone in Studio 66 but joined by CBS' Will Brinson and Sports Illustrated's Nick Kostos via Skype! The guys first get into the New York Giants personnel decision making as of late and if they could be a contender, since Kostos is a big Giants fan (4:36). Then, on the heels of Carson Wentz being talked about as a strong MVP candidate, they give their very early picks for 2019 NFL MVP (15:06). Next, the trio talks about the merits of Eli Manning's career including comparing him to his draft class-mates, Ben Roethlisberger and Phil Rivers (23:50). Finally, Shek, Brinson and Kostos round out the show with some 2019 QB either or's (55:45).
